      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON STELLA (6) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this track and trip which boasts five wins and seven placings. In the money last time at Murray Bridge (22.70) in a Grade 6, finishing a 2 length second. Looks suited and should go close. FANTASTIC ADA (4) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in five starts, including three wins and two placings. Hit the frame latest (23.37) when second at this track in a OPEN. Can feature with the right run. MAGIC NANCY (1) doesn't have the best strike-rate. Finished in the money last time though when second (23.47) at this track. Can measure up. IVORY PYGMY (8) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
